text: BBC Radio 1's Live Lounge 2014 is a compilation album consisting of live tracks played on Fearne Cotton's BBC Radio 1 show, both cover versions and original songs. The album was released on 27 October 2014, and is the tenth in the series of Live Lounge albums. ==Track listing== == References == Category:2014 compilation albums Category:2014 live albums Category:Live Lounge Category:Covers albums Category:Rhino Entertainment compilation albums Category:Sony Music compilation albums Category:Universal Music Group compilation albums Category:Universal Music TV albums
